abstract: New Zealand beats Argentina, 26-16, in Rugby World Cup match in London.
lead_paragraph: A record crowd for a Rugby World Cup match saw a classic as Argentina pushed New Zealand before the All Blacks earned a 26-16 win in front of almost 90,000 fans at Wembley Stadium in London.
